  "recipeInstructions": "1. Combine first 13 ingredients in a food processor.\nProcess on/off turns until finely chopped.\n2. Transfer to a bowl and cover.\n3. Chill at least 4 hours, or make up to two days ahead.\n4. Mix in the chopped cilantro.\n5. Serve with tortilla chips.",
